izes! We hold a wagering license applicable to all Australian states and territories issued by the Norfolk Island Gaming Authority.</p> <p>Our goal is to increase fan engagement in Australian sports and the help grow participation in crowd attendance, viewership and club membership.</p> <p>Being the first of its kind in Australia. We want to provide unique one-day fantasy sport contests in sporting codes such as NRL, AFL, EPL, NFL, RWC, NBA, Big Bash, ODI and T20i. With {{siteUri}} we offer multiple contest types to choose from. These include head to head, system created leagues, and if none of those appeal to you, you can create your own (See <a ui-sref="help">FAQ</a> for more info). We want to give you full control of your team. You pick the players you want while having the chance to win instant cash prizes!</p> <p>Didnt win? Dont worry! What makes us unique is you can always play tomorrow or next week to make amends. With no season long commitment, it doesnt matter how well or how badly you went yesterday, you always have another opportunity tomorrow!</p> <p>Be part of the Australian revolution in fantasy sports! <a ui-sref="signup.me">sign up</a> now!</p> <h2>Our Sports</h2> <div class="row text-center"> <div class="col-xs-4 col-md-2" title="National Rugby League"> <div class="sport-large"><i class="mb-icon mb-icon-sport-nrl"></i></div> <div>NRL</div> <div>National Rugby League</div> </div> <div class="col-xs-4 col-md-2" title="Australian Football League"> <div class="sport-large"><i class="mb-icon mb-icon-sport-afl"></i></div> <div>AFL</div> <div>Australian Football League</div> </div> <div class="col-xs-4 col-md-2" title="English Premiere League"> <div class="sport-large"><i class="mb-icon mb-icon-sport-epl"></i></div> <div>EPL</div> <div>English Premiere League</div> </div> <div class="col-xs-4 col-md-2" title="National Football League"> <div class="sport-large"><i class="mb-icon mb-icon-sport-nfl"></i></div> <div>NFL</div> <div>National Football League</div