                                                                            a.put("views/account/verification.html",'<div> <dl class="dl-horizontal"> <h2>You\'re good to go</h2> <p>You can now enter fantasy sports contests using your deposited funds.</p> <div ng-show="account.member.memberVerifications.verified === \'VERIFIED\'"> <p>Your identity has been verified with our partners using D&B GreenID, but you will still need to verify your drivers license, passport or proof of age card and within a month of joining you will need to verify your credit card also. You\'ll be able to make your first deposit and play, but you won\'t be able to withdraw until you take this step.</p> <p>You can send through a \'close up\' of each before you make your next deposit or withdrawal.<br><br></p> </div> <div ng-show="account.member.memberVerifications.verified !== \'VERIFIED\' &amp;&amp; account.member.memberVerifications.verified !== true"> <p>You will however need to verify your identification, credit card, and supply us with a close up of each. You must do this within 90 days of joining, and won\'t be able to withdraw funds until you do.<br><br></p> </div> <h4 ng-show="account.member.memberVerifications.verified !== \'VERIFIED\' &amp;&amp; ((account.member.joinDate | amDifference : null : \'days\') >= -90)">You have <strong class="text-danger">{{90 + (account.member.joinDate | amDifference : null : \'days\') }} days</strong> to complete the following verification steps:<br><br></h4> <h4 ng-show="account.member.memberVerifications.verified !== \'VERIFIED\' &amp;&amp; ((account.member.joinDate | amDifference : null : \'days\') < -90)"><strong class="text-danger">You have exceeded 90 days without verifying your address and/or photo ID.</strong><br><br></h4> <!-- Identity --> <div class="row form-group" data-ng-if="!myDetailsDefined"> <div class="col-sm-6"> <div class="numberCircle">1</div> <span>Verify Identity</span> </div> <div class="col-sm-6"> <button class="btn btn-primary" ui-sref="account.details">Do this now</button> </div> </div> <div class="row form-group" data-ng-if="myDetailsDefined"> <div class="col-sm-6"> <div class="numberCircle">1</div> <span ng-show="account.member.memberVerifications.verified === \'VERIFIED\'"> Green ID identification check </span> <span ng-show="account.member.memberVerifications.verified !== \'VERIFIED\'"> Proof of Address </span> </div> <div class="col-sm-6"> <div class="clearfix" data-upload-verification-doc data-url="apiEndpoint + \'/members/verification\'" data-status="account.member.memberVerifications.verified"> </div> <a class="upload-instructions" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#verifyModal">What should my proof of address look like?</a> </div> </div> <div class="row form-group"> <div class="col-sm-6"> <div class="numberCircle">2</div> \'Closeup\' of drivers license, passport, or proof of age card </div> <div class="col-sm-6" data-upload-verification-doc data-url="apiEndpoint + \'/members/closeup\'" data-status="account.member.memberVerifications.closeupVerified"> </div> </div> <div class="row form-group"> <div class="col-sm-6"> <div class="numberCircle">3</div> Email Verification </div> <div class="col-sm-6"> <div ng-show="!account.member.memberVerifications.emailVerified"> Please verify your email by clicking on the link in the confirmation email you received from us after signup. </div> <div ng-show="account.member.memberVerifications.emailVerified" class="is-verified"> <i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i> Verified </div> </div> </div> <div ng-show="account.cards.length > 0"> <h4>We also require verification of your credit card to keep depositing and withdrawing:</h4> <div ng-repeat="card in account.cards"> <div class="row form-group"> <div class="col-sm-6"> <div class="numberCircle">{{$index + 4}}</div> \'Closeup\' of credit card <div style="margin-left: 5%">{{card.scheme}}: {{card.ccNumber}}</div> </div> <div class="col-sm-6" data-upload-verification-doc data-url="apiEndpoint + \'/members/card/\' + card.id + \'/closeup\'" data-status="card.closeupVerified"> &nbsp;<a style="cursor: pointer" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#closeupModal">What should my close ups look like?</a> </div> </div> </div> <p><a data-toggle="modal" data-target="#verifyModalCC">Why do I need my identity and credit card verified?</a> </p> </div> <div class="row form-group" ng-show="bankAccount"> <h4 class="brand-primary">Lastly, before you withdraw money, you will need to verify any bank account you want to withdraw to</h4> <div class="col-sm-6"> <div class="numberCircle">6</div> A scanned copy of your bank account statement (showing name, address, bsb, account #) </div> <div class="col-sm-6" data-upload-verification-doc data-url="apiEndpoint + \'/members/accountverification\'" data-status="account.member.memberVerifications.accountVerified"> </div> </div> <br><br> <p> <button ng-show="allVerified" class="btn btn-default" ui-sref="lobby">Done</button> <button ng-show="!allVerified" class="btn btn-default" ui-sref="lobby">Do the rest later</button> </p> </dl> <!-- Modal --> </div> <div class="modal fade" id="verifyModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabel" aria-hidden="true"> <div class="modal-dialog"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-header"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button> <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabel">Certified Documentation</h4> </div> <div class="modal-body"> <p>A certified document is an official document showing your address which has been sighted and verified (signed) by an authorsed person.</p> <p>See a full list of authorised persons below.</p> <h4>Your options are:</h4> <p> <div class="numberCircle">1</div> A valid copy of a photo ID that also shows your address (drivers license, proof of age card, passport) </p> <p class="text-center"> OR </p> <p> <div class="numberCircle">2</div> One other documents, of which must show your address (ie, telephone bill, credit card statement, bank statement, tax office notice, rates bill, water or gas bill) </p> <p> Make sure your document shows: </p> <p> <ul> <li>your full name and address</li> <li>shows the same address you provided us on the registration page</li> <li>is not older than 6 months</li> </ul> </p> <p>We cannot accept documents that do not meet this criteria.</p>  </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="modal fade" id="selfieModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="selfieLabel" aria-hidden="true"> <div class="modal-dialog"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-header"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button> <h4 class="modal-title" id="selfieLabel">What should my selfies look like?</h4> </div> <div class="modal-body"> <p>Take one close up photo of your drivers license, proof of age or passport, and another of your credit card. These should be the same cards used for the \'selfies\' </p> <p> These should look like this: </p> <div class="row"> <div class="col-sm-6"> <img width="300" src="images/selfie.jpg"> </div> <p> <div class="col-sm-6"> <ul> <li>Your face clearly visible</li> <li>Your card clearly visible, and the same one used in your \'close ups\'</li> </ul> </div> </p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="modal fade" id="closeupModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="closeupLabel" aria-hidden="true"> <div class="modal-dialog"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-header"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button> <h4 class="modal-title" id="closeupLabel">What should my closeups look like?</h4> </div> <div class="modal-body"> <p>Please take a close-up of your credit card.</p> <p>These should look like this:</p> <div class="row"> <div class="col-sm-6"> <div class="card-image"></div> <!--<img width="300" src="images/card.jpg"/>--> </div> <div class="col-sm-6"> <ul> <li>Your card details are clearly visible</li> <li>For credit cards, our name, and card number and valid dates clearly visible</li> <li>Your photo ID (driver license, Proof of age card, passport) should clearly show your name, date of birth, and photo </li> </ul> </div> </div> <div class="row"> <div class="col-sm-12"> <p>Please note: once {{siteUri}} has sighted your credit card images, they will be deleted and not stored.</p> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> </div> <div class="modal fade" id="verifyModalCC" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="myModalLabelCC" aria-hidden="true"> <div class="modal-dialog"> <div class="modal-content"> <div class="modal-header"> <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"><span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span></button> <h4 class="modal-title" id="myModalLabelCC">Verifying your ID</h4> </div> <div class="modal-body"> <p>You will need to have your identity verified within 90 days of joining {{siteUri}}.</p> <p>Until you are verified, although you will be able to deposit funds and enter contests, you will not be able to withdraw funds from your account or make any further deposits.</p> <p>If after 90 days you have still not verified your ID, then your account will be suspended, meaning you will not be able to enter contests, deposit funds or withdraw funds.</p> <p>See our <a ui-sref="terms-and-conditions">full terms and conditions</a> for more information on account verification</p> </div> </div> </div> </div>'),a.put("views/account/wallet.html",'<h3>Wallet</h3> <p><span class="wallet-label">Current Balance:</span><strong>{{walletLog.currentBalance.amount | money: walletLog.currentBalance.currency}}</strong></p> <p data-ng-if="bonusBalance.amount > 0"><span class="wallet-label">Bonus Balance:</span><strong>{{bonusBalance.amount | money: bonusBalance.currency}}</strong></p> <div class="form-group"> <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" ui-sref="withdr